    "key": "output|After_choosing_your_new_tongue_type_you_crack_open_the_can_Bot|1e59447e85af",
    "original": "After choosing your new tongue type, you crack open the can. Bottoms up! The drink tastes like a knockoff cola, though admittedly it’s pretty tasty. Once the can is empty, you toss it.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "<<POS:09953370>>"
  },
  {
    "key": "output|After_a_few_moments_you_look_at_your_codex_to_check_how_much_ti|49f5153d5979",
    "original": "After a few moments, you look at your codex to check how much time has elapsed since you drank the cola. It’s only been about a minute, but it feels like it’s been longer... Was it a dud? Suddenly, your tongue wiggles around involuntarily in your mouth, catching you off guard. You can feel it gradually heating up, like you just ate something spicy. The urge to open your lips for relief is overwhelming, but that might not be the best idea while the microsurgeons are doing their work.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "<<POS:09953569>>"
  },
  {
    "key": "output|Once_the_odd_sensation_fades_away_you_turn_on_your_Codex_s_came|1bb7525a601e",
    "original": "Once the odd sensation fades away, you turn on your Codex’s camera and stick your tongue out at it, taking in its new form! <b>You now have a \"+t+\" tongue.</b>",
